{
  "id": "adv_main_02_10_01",
  "title": "東京編2章21話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-host001.m4a",
      "text": "勝者は……TRINITYAiLE！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The winner is… TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.3333334000004,
          "startTime": 4.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "三回戦、やっぱり\nTRINITYAiLEが勝ちましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as I thought‚ TRINITYAiLE\nwon the third round as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "それも、圧倒的大差で……\n他の事務所なら間違いなくシードね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And by a considerable margin…\nAny other agency and they would definitely be the seeded group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、さすが瑠依ちゃん達だね\nテレビで観てても、つい声を出して応援しちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Rui‚ Yu‚ and Sumire are incredible.\nI can’t help but cheer out loud when I see them on TV.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "当然よ。トリエルは私達を倒したんだから\nこんなところで負けたら、許さないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Since TRINITYAiLE defeated us‚\nI wouldn’t forgive them if they lost at this stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "順当にいけば、次はいよいよスリクス……\nプレタポルテのアイドル同士の戦いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like they’ll be up against IIIX next…\nA battle between the idols of Pret-A-Porter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスが三回戦で消えるとは思えない\nほぼ100％、トリエルの次の相手はスリクスだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s hard to imagine IIIX losing in the third round.\nIt’s almost 100% guaranteed that TRINITYAiLE’s next opponent is IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの頂点、BIG4の一角と\nついに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One of the pillars of the BIG4‚ standing at the top of the idol industry.\nFinally…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "事務所は別々になっちゃったけど\n瑠依ちゃん達には負けてほしくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We may be in separate agencies now‚\nbut I don’t want TRINITYAiLE to lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私達、月のテンペストの次の相手は、勝った方になる\n私も、瑠依さん達と同じステージに立ちたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest will compete against whichever group wins.\nI want to stand on the same stage as TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスは強いわ……でも今のトリエルには勢いがある\nもしかしたら勝てるかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX is strong… but TRINITYAiLE has momentum right now.\nThey may be able to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、さくら、貴方達は、もうレッスンに行きなさい\n瑠依達に負けないように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ Sakura‚ all of you need to head to your lesson.\nMake sure you don’t lose to Rui and the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、今のトリエルは凄い。神がかっていると）\n（言ってもいい。でも、だからこそ、あの人が……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Yes‚ TRINITYAiLE is doing incredible. You could even say)\n(they’re performing on another level. But I doubt she’ll stand for it…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 94
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk001.m4a",
      "text": "悪かったわね、急に呼び出して\n……ああ、まだ言ってなかったわね、ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for calling you here out of the blue.\nOh‚ excuse me‚ where are my manners.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk002.m4a",
      "text": "四回戦進出、おめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations on making it to the fourth round.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ観てたんですね。てっきり姫野さんは\nうちらなんか興味ないと思ってたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? So you were watching. I was under the impression\nyou didn’t have any interest in us‚ Ms. Himeno.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ、優ちゃん、はっきり言い過ぎだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yu‚ don’t be so blunt…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "――ありがとうございます\nそれで、私達に緊急の話とはなんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nSo what was this urgent talk you wanted to have with us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "なるべく手短にお願いします\nレッスンに戻りたいので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please be as brief as possible.\nWe want to get back to our lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、私もまどろっこしいのは嫌いだわ\nビジネスはスピードが大切だものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Agreed. I don’t like to beat around the bush either.\nSpeed is essential in business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk004.m4a",
      "text": "では、単刀直入に……四回戦、貴方達は\nスリクスに負けなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let me get to the point… For the fourth round‚\nI want you to lose to IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 140.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　ど、どうしてですか！？\nそれどういう意味ですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?! Wh-why?!\nWhat’re you talking about?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "八百長や、すみれちゃん\nもしかしたら……とは思ってたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She wants to fix the match‚ Sumire.\nI thought this might happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "八百長って……どうして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fix the match? Why…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "今、私達TRINITYAiLEは調子がいい\n大番狂わせでスリクスを倒す可能性が出てきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE has momentum right now.\nThere’s a chance we could actually beat IIIX in a big upset.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、そうなっては困る人がいる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But a result like that would inconvenience some people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "この事務所の偉い人達\n――目の前の姫野さんとかやろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The higher-ups in the agency.\nPeople like Ms. Himeno right here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな！\nスリクスも私達も同じ事務所なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but why?\nWe’re in the same agency as IIIX…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk005.m4a",
      "text": "誤解しないで、私は決して貴方達を\n軽視している訳じゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t get me wrong. I’m in no way\nunderestimating all of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk006.m4a",
      "text": "だけどTRINITYAiLEは、プレタポルテの\nこのアイドル業界の看板を背負うにはまだ早過ぎる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s still too early for TRINITYAiLE\nto be the face of Pret-A-Porter in the idol industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、スリクスに勝ちを譲って\n私達は二番手に甘んじろと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you want us to hand over the win to IIIX\nand settle for second place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk007.m4a",
      "text": "私に従うなら、これからは貴方達を\n事務所総出でバックアップしてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you follow my instructions‚ you’ll have\nthe agency’s full backing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk008.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロよりも……いいえ、バンプロに居たころよりも\nずっと上を目指せるわ。だから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll be able to aim higher than you ever could’ve in Hoshimi Productions…\nor even Van Productions‚ for that matter‚ so—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 208.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
