      "text": "トリエルはみんなにエールを送るアイドルなんです！\nなのに、わざと手を抜くなんて絶対に出来ません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is a group that cheers everyone on to do their best!\nThere’s no way we’ll intentionally give a lukewarm performance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 225.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
