      "text": "予想通りの反応ね。すみれはやっぱりまだ子供ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just the reaction I expected. You really are still a child‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
