      "text": "それとな、姫野さん\nうちも今猛烈に怒ってるで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ and by the way‚ Ms. Himeno‚\nI’m also absolutely furious right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 249.2057647705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-krk010.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依はどうなの？\nここに移籍を決めた貴方なら――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about you‚ Rui?\nYou were the one who decided to transfer here—",
