    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "私達は実力で、アイドルのトップに立ちます\nそれ以外の道はありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We will rise to the top as idols based on our own abilities.\nThat is the only path for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.4744964599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "私は、そのために星見プロのみんなと別れて……\n優とすみれも巻き込んで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For that‚ I parted ways with everyone at Hoshimi Productions…\nand even got Yu and Sumire mixed up in all this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.5411631266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.3744964599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "私は……私達は勝ちます\nあなたの思い通りになんて、絶対にさせない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… we will win.\nWe will never let you have your way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 277.0411631266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 281.0078297932
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
